			Point of Interest
			
	*Fragran Cannion : is the third area and leads to the shores in the west side of the continent. Is located in the east side and is the smallest area.
		*Maldiff Oasis : is a giant oasis located in the west side delimitating this area from "Crystal Desert".
		*Ranpold Finger Path : is the main location that starts from the west side and leads to the depts of the labyrinth ahead.
		*Labyrinth of Ranpold : east side of the cannion here is transforms into a maze for the momst part of the area and leads to the shore far in east.
			*Eastport Piers : located at the east side of the region, the port here is surrounded by the mountains that separate de regions.
				*Sunnywave Tavern : located near the shore, in "Eastport Piers" this tavern is the ideal spot for adventures to end their travels to, for rest and for new adventures that comes ahead.